reviewText: Great show  but be advised this is the UK version, not the Southwest Airlines USA version
Always been a fan of the show.
This is the BRITISH SHOW-EASY JET it is NOT the Southwest AIRLINE show that is in the US-they musy have copied it for overseas-be careful when ordering.

Good video quality.  Good communication between myself and seller.  I did not realize the video was being shipped from outside the US; so it took much longer to receive than expected. The seller was kind and explained things to me when I had a concern.  I would recommend.
I found it difficult to locate the British Airline episodes.  These DVDs are excellent.
